1. *Smatraju* da je ovo najbolji način (They *believe* this is the best way)
2. Mi *smatramo* da je ovo dobra ideja (We *think* this is a good idea)
3. Oni *smatraju* da treba da se promeni strategija (They *consider* that the strategy needs to be changed)
4. Neki ljudi *smatraju* da je to nemoguće (Some people *think* that this is impossible)
5. *Smatrajte* to urađenim (Consider it done)
6. Ja *smatram* da je ovo pogrešno (I *believe* this is wrong)
7. Kako *smatraš* da treba da reagujemo? (How do *you think* we should react?)
8. Svi *smatraju* da je to pravedno (Everyone *considers* it fair)
9. *Smatrajući* da nema alternative, odlučio je da pristane (Believing that there was no alternative, he decided to agree)
10. *Smatrajmo* to samo kao preliminarni plan (Let's just *consider* it as a preliminary plan)